    "asOf": "2009-05-12",
    "date": "2009-06-02T21:15:22Z",
    "text": "Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to require that a nonimmigrant foreign student seeking to enter the United States to study at a language training program enroll at a language program that is accredited by an accrediting agency recognized by the Secretary of Education.\n\nProvides for a specified three-year exception to such requirement."
